// Item_Energizer
Item_Energizer_name												Energizer
Item_Energizer_description										
Item_Energizer_description_simple								Activate to grant 50 Movement Speed and 25 Attack Speed to nearby allies for 6 seconds.
Item_Energizer_search_terms										energizer,support,strength,str,agility,agi,intelligence,int,stats,movespeed,movement,drum,drums,drumofendurance,endurance
Item_Energizer_IMPACT_effect									Активируйте, чтобы предоставить союзникам в радиусе ^o50 скорости передвижения и 25 скорости атаки^* на ^o6 секунд^*.\n\nЮниты, не управляемые игроком, получают возможность передвижения по единицам.
Item_Energizer_shop_categories									Filter_Strength,Filter_Agility,Filter_Intelligence,Filter_Activatable,Filter_Mobility
Item_Energizer_shop_flavor										Craving power without end, Newerth's best magicians finally evoked this mystical artifact. Although simple of design, this device enabled both the Hellbourne hordes and the Legion armies to move with speed unparalleled by anything known before. The appearance of Blitz was only a natural consequence, perceiving a challenge he could best.
Item_Energizer_tooltip_flavor									Дань уважения DivA за его забавное внедрение героев в игру!\n\n..и Яркому диктору, потому что он такой DivA!

