Item_MinorTotem_search_terms									minortotem,minor,ironwoodbranch,ironwood,branch,ironbranch,ggbranch,totem,strength,str,agility,agi,intelligence,int,totem,mt,ib,iwb,1s,1a									
Item_MinorTotem_effect_header									Status Effect(s)
