Item_RingOfTheTeacher_effect_header									Status Effect(s)
Item_RingOfTheTeacher_shop_flavor										Many sages who ply the mystic arts take on apprentices from time to time. In such cases, Rings of the Teacher are commonly seen flashing on their fingers, for these curious relics restore the magical powers of those around the wielder and provide a small defensive aura to protect against misfiring rituals. They also give off a small electrical charge for chastising idle pupils, a popular feature.
