Item_Firebrand_description2										Бонус ^yСкорости передвижения^* этого предмета не суммируется ни с самим собой, ни с предметами, в которые он встроен.
Item_Firebrand_description_simple								^oМодификатор Firebrand^*\nПовышает вашу ловкость, скорость передвижения и скорость атаки.
Item_Firebrand_search_terms										firebrand,slash,yasha,agility,movementspeed,movespeed,mobility,attackspeed,as,fb
Item_Firebrand_effect_header										Status Effect(s)
Item_Firebrand_shop_flavor										Slash is an assassin's dagger that gives one the agility and attacking speed to inflict quick, accurate blows, and the Movement Speed to escape afterwards.  Despite these helpful traits, the weapon itself inflicts little damage, and is perhaps most effective as a charm.
Item_Firebrand_shop_categories									Filter_Agility,Filter_Mobility,Filter_AttackSpeed
