// Item_AmuletOfExile
Item_AmuletOfExile_name											Amulet of Exile
Item_AmuletOfExile_description									Gain 3 mana per Enemy unit killed.
Item_AmuletOfExile_description_simple							3 Сила\n3 Ловкость\n6 Интеллект
Item_AmuletOfExile_search_terms									talismanofexile,exile,talismanexile,nulltalisman,toe,nt,strength,agility,intelligence,aoe,amuletofexile
Item_AmuletOfExile_effect_header								Status Effect(s)
Item_AmuletOfExile_shop_flavor									Those who fail in the study of Newerth's secrets, yet nevertheless find favor in the eyes of their masters, are often given Talismans of Exile. These bestow modest magical strength fit for an apprentice as well as certain limited powers that might help the exiled one survive in a hostile world.
